## Comprehensive Pricing Page Analysis

### 1. **PricingPage.js** — Plan Structure & Features

#### **PLAN_META Definition** (Lines 11-16)
```javascript
const PLAN_META = [
  { id: 'free',      price: 0,   featureCount: 4, lockedCount: 4, hasBadge: false, highlight: false, priceId: null },
  { id: 'grow',      price: 19,  featureCount: 7, lockedCount: 0, hasBadge: true,  highlight: true,  priceId: process.env.REACT_APP_STRIPE_GROW_PRICE_ID },
  { id: 'scale',     price: 49,  featureCount: 7, lockedCount: 0, hasBadge: true,  highlight: false, priceId: process.env.REACT_APP_STRIPE_SCALE_PRICE_ID },
  { id: 'evolution', price: 99,  featureCount: 8, lockedCount: 0, hasBadge: true,  highlight: false, priceId: process.env.REACT_APP_STRIPE_EVOLUTION_PRICE_ID },
];
```

**Plan Summary:**
- **Free**: €0/month → 4 features, 4 locked items, NO badge, NOT highlighted
- **Grow**: €19/month → 7 features, 0 locked, HAS badge, HIGHLIGHTED (primary call-to-action)
- **Scale**: €49/month → 7 features, 0 locked, HAS badge, NOT highlighted
- **Evolution**: €99/month → 8 features, 0 locked, HAS badge, NOT highlighted

#### **Comparison Table** (Lines 19-32)
Defines 12 feature rows comparing all 4 plans with values like:
- "unlimited", "trial", "partial", "email", "priority", "dedicated", "addon"
- Icons: ✅ (included), ❌ (not included), ⚠️ (warning), 🔒 (locked)

#### **Plan Card JSX Structure** (Lines 137-209)

Each plan card renders:

```javascript
<motion.div className={`pricing__plan 
  ${plan.highlight ? 'pricing__plan--highlight' : ''} 
  ${subscription === plan.id ? 'pricing__plan--current' : ''}`}>

  {/* Glow effect (highlight plans only) */}
  {plan.highlight && <div className="pricing__plan-glow" />}

  {/* Badge (hasBadge plans, not current) */}
  {plan.hasBadge && subscription !== plan.id && (
    <div className="pricing__plan-badge">
      {t(`pricing.plan.${plan.id}.badge`)}
    </div>
  )}

  {/* Current plan indicator */}
  {subscription === plan.id && (
    <div className="pricing__plan-badge pricing__plan-badge--current">
      {t('pricing.currentPlan', { defaultValue: '✅ Current Plan' })}
    </div>
  )}

  {/* Header: Name + Description */}
  <div className="pricing__plan-header">
    <h2 className="pricing__plan-name">{t(`pricing.plan.${plan.id}.name`)}</h2>
    <p className="pricing__plan-desc">{t(`pricing.plan.${plan.id}.desc`)}</p>
  </div>

  {/* Price */}
  <div className="pricing__plan-price">
    <span className="pricing__plan-amount">€{plan.price}</span>
    <div className="pricing__plan-period">
      {plan.price === 0 ? 'forever free' : '/month'}
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* CTA Button */}
  <button className={`btn 
    ${plan.highlight ? 'btn-primary' : 'btn-secondary'} 
    pricing__plan-cta`}>
    {getPlanCta(plan)}
  </button>

  {/* Features List */}
  <div className="pricing__features">
    {features.map((f) => (
      <div className="pricing__feature pricing__feature--included">
        <span className="pricing__feature-icon">✅</span>
        <span>{f}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
    {locked.map((f) => (
      <div className="pricing__feature pricing__feature--locked">
        <span className="pricing__feature-icon">🔒</span>
        <span>{f}</span>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</motion.div>
```

